* Testing Pyramid
** Unit Tests (Base)
***_ Individual functions
***_ Fast: milliseconds
***_ Many tests
** Integration Tests
***_ Component interactions
***_ Moderate: seconds
***_ Fewer tests
** End-to-End Tests
***_ Complete workflows
***_ Slower: minutes
***_ Small number
** UAT (Top)
***_ Business requirements
***_ Stakeholder validation
***_ Varies in speed
@endmindmap
